{"tid":439244,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"對個內向仔有feel想識佢","createTime":"2017-10-17T15:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T12:34:44.000Z","uid":124514,"like":38,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"240448a1aae859da48efea0c5686246eb99faf8b","tid":439244,"uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:36:11.000Z","msg":"由yr1開始已經覺得佢好特別<br />\n應該話佢d舉動怪怪地<br />\n成日行樓梯檻級勁大步又好嘈<br />\n開門又唔係用手推係用腳踢<br />\n成日自己喺到笑咁(佢玩電話)<br />\n上堂同食飯都係自己一個<br />\n到依家yr4都仲係自己一個<br />\n大家覺得佢係個咩人?<br />\n我冇同佢傾過計<br />\n其實我好想識佢<br />\n但係佢係個好靜嘅人<br />\n又唔知點樣可以同佢搭訕<br />\n大家有咩建議<br />\n對佢有d feel <br />\n想由朋友做起(首先係八下佢有冇女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n不過佢咁獨來獨往又好似唔會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感覺佢係個好專一既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA0女想識個男朋友仔阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5c4137aa436f6da2bb6621a8125c3a495377f4","tid":439244,"uid":30751,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:37:19.000Z","msg":"真毒都有人留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee36058446dfd0f15799bee9f2e16316faa5b3c8","tid":439244,"uid":44504,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁似講緊我"},{"pid":"ab87cd71573c34b0a97d61951e24e0f5e29ac446","tid":439244,"uid":125079,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:40:18.000Z","msg":"你竟然留意咗人四年都冇主動聊過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試下扮問功課野或者分組，上堂扮遲入只可以坐佢隔離，再借啲意問佢借文具，再問問聊佢講野"},{"pid":"1e79097932d7e78e74cd728156a112b8d8dd133a","tid":439244,"uid":21423,"like":9,"dislike":34,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:40:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53b63027bfcd639c2c3e5a68254658c996a4ccbc","tid":439244,"uid":124514,"like":0,"d